# This systemtest create job record with 1,2 file but 0 bytes
# Consolidation in that case was failing with 
# 
# Version: 24.0.3~pre0.54685a85d (27 March 2025) Ubuntu 22.04.5 LTS
#bareos-dir JobId 103069: Start Virtual Backup JobId 103069, Job=sch-hp-desktop-Users-Pictures.2025-04-16_08.52.03_37
#bareos-dir JobId 103069: Unable to get Job record. ERR=cats/sql_get.cc:267 No Job found for JobName ''
#bareos-dir JobId 103069: No files found to read. No bootstrap file written.
#bareos-dir JobId 103069: Fatal error: Could not create bootstrap file
#bareos-dir JobId 103069: Replicating deleted files from jobids 101984,102016,102055,102099 to jobid 103069
#bareos-dir JobId 103069: Error: Bareos myth-dir 24.0.3~pre0.54685a85d (27Mar25):
#102908 | sch-hp-desktop-Users-Pictures | sch-hp-desktop-fd | 2025-03-22 01:51:07 | 00:01:10 | B | F | 42,740 | 384,907,132,555 | T |
#101984 | sch-hp-desktop-Users-Pictures | sch-hp-desktop-fd | 2025-03-23 02:41:40 | 00:01:07 | B | I | 1 | 0 | T |
